column2: A blazing fast masonry layout generator for fixed width elements.

column5:
Merge pull request #41 from santi6291/master

update size options description on README
upgrade/fix the demo site (and version the deps)
remove dist file, and swap gulp for rollup
add mkdirp to gulpfile (not async, omg)

update license, and demo site

Merge pull request #21 from callmecavs/build-system

upgrade build system

Merge pull request #18 from scarletsky/slice-sizes

avoid mutation of sizes parameter
Fix should not mutate original sizes
add default value for resize, to not break API
add support for removing resize handler

update solution bullet point on site
add site title, update made by link
add npm script to deploy project site
update gulpfile to add file for site

use ES6 syntax for return object
change media query -> breakpoint in README

fix API section headings in README

abstract function series from pack/update methods
change resize handler to use rAF
add packed attr handling, improve commenting
udpate test file to include timing and stress test
